                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        <p>The Output Type defines the format of the AI’s response. Whether the result is plain text, HTML, JSON, or code, specifying the output type ensures that the GPT produces content that can be directly utilized in the intended application or platform.</p>
                                        <p>This parameter is key for integration with other systems, enabling the GPT to deliver responses that require minimal post-processing, thus enhancing efficiency and usability in practical scenarios.</p>
                                    </div>
