                                        <p>The choice of model determines the capabilities and accuracy of the GPT. Different models, like GPT-3 or GPT-4, have varying degrees of complexity and understanding, which can significantly impact the quality of the AI’s responses.</p>
                                        <p>Selecting the appropriate model is essential for tasks that require high precision or creative output, ensuring that the AI can meet or exceed the expectations for its performance in specific contexts.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Temperature -->
                            <div class="accordion-item">
